                    </ol>
                    <p>We collect device and connection-specific information when you install, access, or use our Services. This includes information like hardware model, operating system information, app version, browser information, connection information including phone number, mobile operator or ISP, language, time zone, IP, device operations information, and identifiers like device identifiers (including identifiers unique to <a href="https://www.equitybankgroup.com/">Unaitas Group and it’s subsidiaries’ products </a>associated with the same device or account).</p>
                    <ol>
